scenes.description: Risu is alone in her room, playing with and eating acorns while talking to the audience.
Risu finds a piggy bank and starts counting the coins inside.
Moona and Iofi arrive and confront Risu about the piggy bank in a comical skit.
The trio performs their unit song 'HI-15'.
